Shouldn't the hook be before

    $text =~ s/\0\0(\d+)\0\0/$things[$1]/eg;
    $text =~ s/$chr1\0/\0/g;

to allow more linkifications? See also bug 652663 (which will probably already add another hook near the end of the subroutine).

